WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.120 --> 00:00:08.120
 Hey. My name is Alexander Parisot. Welcome to Bologne in France. 

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:11.800
 Here is the brand new FH adorned as a tribute to Rihanna. 

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:22.280
 I love her music and everything about her. 

00:00:23.360 --> 00:00:26.680
 Here we have two pictures - 

00:00:26.760 --> 00:00:29.880
 - one of her face and one of her in full shape. 

00:00:29.960 --> 00:00:32.920
 The picture is taken at a Rihanna concert. 

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:37.480
 It's the R in Rihanna's name. I like the side best. 

00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:45.840
 We have extra light here, so it looks better 

00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:48.920
 -and so it fits the stainless steel here on the side. 

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:56.080
 In the picture you can see the details clearly - see for example her eyes 

00:00:56.160 --> 00:00:58.160
 - nail polish and shoes. 

00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:02.200
 We have also added a console behind- 

00:01:02.280 --> 00:01:06.480
 -so you get it all together. 

00:01:06.560 --> 00:01:12.640
 We included red LED lights, also around the cabin. 

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:17.320
 The truck has a total of 74 LED lamps. 

00:01:17.400 --> 00:01:21.240
 When everyone is on, it reminds her of her concerts. 

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:27.800
 I think the truck is best at dusk- 

00:01:27.880 --> 00:01:31.680
 -When the LED lights really highlight the entire vehicle. 

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:34.200
 It gives me tears in my eyes. 

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:48.560
 First, the truck should be red- 

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:52.400
 - as it is now, but without the pictures. Just red. 

00:01:52.480 --> 00:01:59.400
 When I turned 40, I held a big party and wanted a trip to the United States. 

00:01:59.480 --> 00:02:04.640
 At the last minute, my wife and I chose to get the truck painted instead. 

00:02:04.720 --> 00:02:08.160
 So it was my gift when I turned 40. 

00:02:08.240 --> 00:02:14.480
 For me it is a dream come true, to run in a painted truck- 

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:16.560
 -for as a child I saw them drive past. 

00:02:16.640 --> 00:02:19.240
 It is my dream that has come true. 

00:02:19.320 --> 00:02:22.480
 Moreover, this theme has never been used before on a truck. 

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:26.200
 The Rihanna theme has never been used before on another truck. 

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:31.160
 It's the first truck ever decorated with Rihanna's image. 

00:02:31.240 --> 00:02:35.520
 It's my album from Rihanna's concert in June 2013. 

00:02:35.600 --> 00:02:38.280
 I was at the concert at Stade de France with my wife. 

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:41.640
 Here is the Stade de France and the ticket. 

00:02:41.720 --> 00:02:44.520
 And inside there are pictures from the concert. 

00:02:44.600 --> 00:02:49.880
 Now I play a bit of my favorite song with Rihanna. 

